data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom French style BEAUTY boasts an open kitchen, dining and living floor plan. The kitchen features custom cabinets, granite counter-tops, and an island with a sit-in bar. The flooring includes wood laminate, tile and carpet throughout. Relax in the primary suite with double vanities in the primary bath. Step outside and enjoy the above ground pool, perfect for entertaining! Don't miss out, schedule your private showing today!
